[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "あれ？　向こうに獣人じゃない方がいますね……\n旅行者でしょうか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00870",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "風の向くまま気の向くまま……\nここで出会うのも運命ってやつかもね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00871",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "変てこ仮面さん！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00872",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "お前、なぜベスティラに？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00873",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "変てこ仮面さんは砂漠でその仮面、\n暑くないんですか？　確実にムレますよね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00874",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "フッ……ファッションっていうのは、\n時として我慢が必要なものなんだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00875",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "おい、話を聞け。タイニーも世間話はいい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00876",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "相変わらず余裕のない人だねえ……\n賞金稼ぎの俺がここにいる理由は１つだけ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00877",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "悪名高い「ヌルスラの鷹」が、ベスティラに\n入国したというネタを掴んだからだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00878",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "「ヌルスラの鷹」……あっ！\n確か、ブラオールの掲示板に載ってた賞金首！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00879",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ここに「ヌルスラの鷹」が……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00880",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "っと、いつになく真剣だね。\nどうしちゃったのさ、タイニー",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_00881",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "タイニーはその賞金首と同郷……\nヌルスラの出身なんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00882",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ヌルスラは最後の島とか墓場島とかいわれる所でね。\n様々な理由で行き場を失った者たちの島なのさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00883",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ありとあらゆる犯罪が横行し、平均寿命も最低の魔窟。\n諸島同盟にも未加入……いや、最近加入したか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00884",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "はい……だから私は、こうして監察官になれたんです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00885",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あー、ごめん。前に変な名前とか言っちゃって……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00886",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "いえ、いいんです。色々言われるのは慣れてますから。\nでも……ヌルスラにもいい人はいるんです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00887",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "私を助けてくれたお兄ちゃんとか……\n治安だって徐々に良くなってる……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00888",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00889",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "それなのに、こういう風に名乗ってる悪い人がいるから\nヌルスラはやっぱり悪い島だ～ってなるんです！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00890",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "あの場所は変わりつつあるんだって示すためにも\n「ヌルスラの鷹」を見つけたら絶対捕まえます！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00891",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "タイニー、気持ちは分かるが本来の目的を忘れるな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00892",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おっと、競争相手を増やしちゃったかな。\nま、その様子じゃ情報も持ってなさそうだし……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00893",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "せいぜい、本来の目的とやらを頑張りなよ。\nあいつの賞金は俺のものだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00894",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "……獣人の行方不明事件に、時を同じくして\n賞金首の入国……か。捜査に思い込みは禁物だが",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00895",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "なんだか匂うね。\nこの線、繋がってんじゃないの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_00896",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そうにしろ、そうじゃないにしろ……\nベスティラ、一筋縄じゃいかなそうな島ね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00897",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ヌルスラ、人攫い……もしかして、あの教団が？\nでも、壊滅したはずじゃ……ざ、残党とか！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00898",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "だとしたら……なおさら絶対に捕まえなきゃ……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00899",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "タイニー……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00900",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]